<a asp-action="Add2">2.) Add Hawaiian Pizza (pineapple and ham, large, thin crust) - $11.49</a><br />
<a asp-action="Add3">3.) Add Meat Pizza (5 meats, large, thin crust) - $13.74(</a><br />
